<plot>When his father Hooper dies, 20 something weakling Frank Chesterfield inherits The Viper Pit, a tough-as-nails biker bar. Clearly a fish out of Water, Frank struggles to earn the respect of the rowdy patrons. Then his greatest challenge bursts through the door: the monstrous Jimbo. In a place where diplomacy doesn't exist, will Frank find a way to fulfill his family legacy and defeat "the meanest biker ever to strap on leathers?" Or will he become just another victime of the legendary bully's path of destruction? He better figure something out quick cause Jimbo's A' Comin'!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?277054</url></doc>
